latestPosts.caption:
“sin miedo, con confianza” - mi Mimita linda ❤️

mi corazón está lleno ❤️ the past few days have been an absolute DREAM 🦋 i am so blessed to be a part of such a rich and vibrant culture 🇳🇮🇪🇨 i am so grateful to have been given the opportunity to speak on my Latine/Hispanic experience with @rarebeauty and connect with so many members of this beautiful community online and in person 🥹❤️ i am in awe of you all and it is a privilege to hear your stories and feel your love! 

thank you to all the hands that touched this campaign and helped bring it to life ❤️ there’s more to share and say but for now i’ll leave it at los amo y muchísimas gracias!! 🥹

#rareconsejos #rarebeauty #hispanicheritagemonth #latineheritagemonth #nicaraguense #ecuatoriana
